Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:45.31,Utama,Kamo,0,0,0,,Kau lumayan juga, temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:52.37,Utama,Kamo,0,0,0,,Siapa sangka si polos Jiro-chan dan\N cabe-cabean terkenal bisa masuk peringkat B suami istri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.32,Utama,Kamo,0,0,0,,Mamamu pasti bangga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.82,Utama,Jiro,0,0,0,,Kau sendiri bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.70,Sign_Basic,text,0,0,0,,{\pos(226.844,74.667)\an4\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0}Kasugahara Kyo\NSangamori Hatsune
