Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.41,Utama,Kamo,0,0,0,,Sekarang peringkat C, jadi tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.99,Utama,Kamo,0,0,0,,Berikutnya, aku akan raih peringkat A!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:08.92,Utama,Kamo,0,0,0,,Saat berganti pasangan, \Npoinnya bisa digabungkan! Untung banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.74,Utama,Jiro,0,0,0,,Watanabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:11.54,Utama,Akari,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.90,Utama,Akari,0,0,0,,Peringkat E?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:14.46,Utama,Jiro,0,0,0,,Eh?
